Commands
	Windows
        H   show/hide top article list
		
    Groups List
        l   toggle display of groups with unread articles
        L   toggle subscribed & list groups with wildcard
        a   add a new group
    Header Window (aka Article List)
		headers/threads
			h	show/hide article window
			t   toggle show all headers
			Esc t	toggle collapse/expand thread
			Esc a	switch header layouts
			x   xpunge - hide articles not marked as important goto
			n   goto to next article, collapsing threads if nec.
			L   goto last read
			,	goto mark
			s/S subject search forward/backward
		marks
			d/u	mark article read/unread
			;	mark
			c/C mark all/all up to current read
			d/u mark delete/undelete
			*   toggle temp. mark important (until group is left) score
			K/v create/view score
    Article pager
        Movement
            <>  top/bottom of message
            T   toggle quotes
            Tab tab paste quotes
            \   toggle signature
            ]   toggle PGP sig
            U   url view
            a   author search forward
        Commands
            f   followup
            F   forward message by email

    Layout/Format
		^/shift^   enlarge/shrink message window
        z       hide/show message window
        h       same for message list
        Esc a     select header formats
        Esc s     select sort method

